  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0bb2\u0bca\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0bb4\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b9a\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0baa\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b8f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd 13 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "13 students were injured in an accident while taking students to school in a lorry",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Thirteen school children have been admitted to hospital after being injured in an accident while transporting students to school in a lorry in the Galenbindunuwewa area in Anuradhapura yesterday (30) morning.",
        "Due to the lack of transport facilities, the accident took place when the rear part of the lorry broke while going to school in a lorry.",
        "Thirty-seven students were traveling in the lorry in the incident and 13 of them were injured and admitted to hospital.",
        "Meanwhile, the local residents have admitted the injured students to Kalenbindunnuwewa Hospital and three students have been shifted to Anuradhapuram Teaching Hospital for further treatment.",
        "Sources at Galenbindunuwewa Hospital said that a student was seriously injured in the leg during the accident. \\",
        "In this case, the Kalenbindunuwewa police are conducting further investigations regarding the accident."
      ],
